      • registerObserver

        public void registerObserver(SOAPListObserver<ResultType,SOAPFaultType> observer)
        Registers an observer for new item, exception and completion events. Note that registering a SOAP11ListObserver (using this method) will result in the observer receiving events on each new item - registering a SOAP11Observer with Request#registerObserver(SOAP11Observer) will only result in it receiving exception and completion.
        Specified by:
        registerObserver in interface ListRequest<ResultType,SOAPFaultType>
        Parameters:
        observer - The observer to register.
